The paper focuses on the detection of manipulated facial images, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for forgery detection, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of spreading false information or fake news, which falls under the category of computer security and cryptography (cs.CR).
